{"tid":1368522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界係冇所謂「和理非回合」，但永遠唔應該出現「群眾鬥群眾」","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:22.000Z","uid":33307,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5685bedf473e53e9b8a383022bd2ec0d9b33326","tid":1368522,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"冇大台，冇咩回合，冇領袖，兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n以上依然使用<br />\n<br />\n但一定要對準政權<br />\n唔好理白衫乜乜乜，有咩就要政權負責<br />\n好似上次單野，白衫亂打人，完全柒晒<br />\n如果出現打交，就會變成「打鬥」<br />\n黑警就扮正義拉兩邊，成為正義化身<br />\n政府就可以置身事外譴責兩邊執雞<br />\n意見就係咁多<br />\n現場決定"},{"pid":"c298ea3cb5aa1d2d470f12142843bc10ebc74d57","tid":1368522,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34cb3824dc484d662593e9173760717ddf4cfcfb","tid":1368522,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c298ea3cb5aa1d2d470f12142843bc10ebc74d57","tid":1368522,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"五大訴求冇要打低黑社會"},{"pid":"06e39239adadd352eda370c7a24c475909a07e5b","tid":1368522,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"7f5881a42d9cd9bd95354490adb8caf13197ba40","tid":1368522,"uid":53915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"其實永遠滿足唔到所有人<br />\n但和理非佔多數 <br />\n所以唔主動進攻已經唔錯<br />\n有人要求客氣對待黑社會 我自己就覺得太over 打不還手真係好on9"},{"pid":"cd5d636fa458f6bc323f105173e3a4d1d49ac18e","tid":1368522,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ddc47c313d9c019f4f9721fb948b8e8e1be1bf7","tid":1368522,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"u r right"},{"pid":"10ad034373e5fab0f8542fc41ae05f4b791a2d16","tid":1368522,"uid":258696,"like":0,